Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to put Chu Tu behind bars, but the operation was a costly one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You destroyed the squatter village,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the government had to relocate the families
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pay damages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the operation, you damaged the shopping centre as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We paid well over a million for the chandelier alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The taxpayers know police work doesn't come cheaply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they don't expect to pay the cost of someone's heroics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you use the stairs? Did you have to destroy that chandelier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always have to be different?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. The force doesn't need superstars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need disciplined policemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, the operation succeeded through team effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not just because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be grateful we didn't fire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bosses wanted you disciplined
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for holding me hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to talk them out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worry about your individualism.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a police officer. Don't forget that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, you're back in uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be assigned wherever needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean he'll be an errand boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'll be very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else do you do besides giving out tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calling all units.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's been a serious road accident at the Industrial Park.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Traffic is at a standstill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All units in the area, please respond.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, go home. I'm working now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of me as a member of the public
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who wants to talk to a policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you look very smart in uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. I'm on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought you a cold drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I can't drink here. - Go on, you need a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have a drink, pretty soon I'll need the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, I'll get into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, superhero! You still haven't been sacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky you're not in jail with Chu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Swiss doctors said I had only three months to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called compassionate release.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three months can pass quickly. Very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My boss will be alive long after you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know you're threatening him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? In that case, he can sue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be careful! Drive on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, Chu Tu is out of jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already knew? That's good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd never nabbed a thief, who would you have to be scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:10:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember, there are 250,000 Royal Hong Kong Police at your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, are there really 250,000 police in Hong Kong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're always recruiting new blood. Didn't you see our newspaper ad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for? Go on patrol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I've talked to Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said you could carry a gun, even after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very happy tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show and dinner were great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You don't seem very happy. - Really? I am happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you had enjoyed it as much as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you worried about Chu? - No. But I'm just being careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Maybe next week... - Hey, superhero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off duty already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What are you doing here? - I can park here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give me a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you must have a nice view from Flat B of the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Am I right? - Go upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find this address?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing what information you can get with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People will do anything for money, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a narrow stairwell in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there ever happened to be a fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would spread quickly through the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the narrow access,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the fire brigade couldn't get in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your girlfriend's cute. You'd better keep a close eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she were to get her pretty ass burnt, it'd ruin her marriage prospects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hero, I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Policemen like me have lots of enemies. You face threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had no enemies, that would mean you'd never caught a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you could stay somewhere else for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me. They're just morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We'd just stand out while they stayed hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then. I'll move to my aunt's and hide out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry too much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you drop a vase on him, I'll definitely be the dead one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on your own? Where's Ka Kui?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not against you dating a policeman,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want him to spend too much time on his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's stubborn, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a man should do his duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he has lots of enemies and you have to move back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I don't worry at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, he doesn't need to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ought to worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who are they? - They're the ones from last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess superhero isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me in the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What do you want? - We have a score to settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to know where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be her mother. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call me a bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong! I'm the bastard son of a bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm not afraid of you. - Don't waste time with him. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Auntie, why has your daughter fallen for a cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That could be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Living on the 19th floor is dangerous, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you took a fall while cleaning the windows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would take more than glue to fix you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Go away! - Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't grab my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, she's just a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count yourself lucky. If you were a man, you'd be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I won't forget this! - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your job that brings the bad guys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. May was badly beaten because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you to stop seeing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did John Ko attack you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started hitting him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just hit me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they knocked me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My backside still hurts. Now I can't sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they know you'd be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They followed her, that's how.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're watching us from across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should go and scold them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's as easy as all that, then I'll be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else do you do besides bullying women?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my favourite hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the law, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may have threatened her, but an arrest requires evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know you're a policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a good reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He reacted like anyone else would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not anyone else. He's a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you've done is disgraceful! It's a disgrace to the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so. If a policeman fails to respond to a personal threat, that's a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And it disgraces the law too. - You're a show-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't let us forget you arrested Chu. How can I explain this to the chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to. I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that will solve the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? This is probably the best solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your support in times past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's your last word...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then try to find a less stressful job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can do anything you want just because you're cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know the law?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat me up just like that! Kill me if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not signing anything. No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sue you for every penny you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got lots of money. I'll get a lawyer. I'll sue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You saw this officer try to assault me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to beat me up like before, when he hit me and broke my glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for that. Would you dare to beat me up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. I'm going to sue you. You're going to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These youngsters have no patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill, why didn't you ask him to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you meant throw him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know what that gesture means, I'll remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want me to be a policeman, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do. I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I have to show for all my time as a cop? Just enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go! That means you've done your job well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a cop has no enemies, there can only be one reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't caught any crooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad they're out to frighten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It proves you're a tough, good cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I resigned today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Really? - Are you disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, all these years I haven't treated you as well as I should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have three month's holiday. Let's go somewhere else to relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, you really mean it? Where to, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bali. - Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't travelled in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, so let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It always feels good to fly on a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That'll be $5,540, please. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Credit card? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's our catalogue, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What clothes should I take?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't need any in Bali.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope they don't rip us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a big company. They're trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's paid for now. Let's cross our fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Fay! - Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Long time no see! Is this your area? - Yes. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've received a bomb threat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Really? - Yeah. Can you help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.05,0:22:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- All right, then. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.85,0:22:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just take a look, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.39,0:22:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in time. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a call about a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's real?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think the guy was kidding. He told us to clear the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The manager said he's nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start clearing the building now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:22:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a hoax, who'll be to blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.91,0:23:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to getting an earful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is real, we'll endanger lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.50,0:23:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider it real.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear the building. Call headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the fire alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.85,0:23:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna set off the fire alarm. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Your baton. - But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! I'll take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.04,0:23:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.71,0:23:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back. I've opened the till already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they paid?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:23:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do? They're not taking any notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.77,0:24:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stay here. Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.48,0:24:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attention please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Evacuate the building.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.11,0:24:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everybody please leave immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.11,0:24:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a fire in the building.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.45,0:24:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please leave now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.45,0:24:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave in an orderly manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everybody outside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.88,0:24:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.80,0:24:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Why is the alarm on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.43,0:24:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about our business?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.10,0:24:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Fay. - What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get them out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.60,0:24:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for your own safety. Go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.52,0:24:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.36,0:24:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be long. You go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.45,0:24:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.51,0:25:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand this. It's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.85,0:25:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who's in charge? - You talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.52,0:25:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave now. The police will take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.48,0:25:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui. Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.11,0:25:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right. You go home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.36,0:25:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.70,0:25:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who made the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.83,0:25:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We received a bomb threat, but we didn't know if it was a hoax.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.25,0:25:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who set off the alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.37,0:25:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.63,0:25:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.05,0:25:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.72,0:25:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, when I was in the Police Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.93,0:26:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was taught that public safety comes first,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.85,0:26:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I set off the alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.93,0:26:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you're indispensable?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.15,0:26:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superintendent, there's no fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.94,0:26:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but your men cleared the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.90,0:26:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The Bomb Disposal Unit is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.32,0:26:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be needed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.07,0:26:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I hope this isn't a hoax.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.33,0:26:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do I, Uncle Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.08,0:26:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raymond, they want to see the head man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.58,0:26:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.50,0:26:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where's the Bomb Disposal Unit? - On their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.00,0:26:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.13,0:26:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.84,0:26:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I do know? Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.38,0:26:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we have to wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.76,0:26:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.64,0:26:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go back in very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.73,0:26:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.29,0:27:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When can we go back in?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.34,0:27:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Now what? - Very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.17,0:27:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Here's your ball, kiddo. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.68,0:27:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.72,0:27:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bomb Disposal Unit is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.02,0:27:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they don't find anything, the boss will blow a fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.73,0:27:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Bill, I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.65,0:27:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.04,0:27:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red alert! All units move in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.33,0:27:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and fight the fire. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.93,0:28:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose the good news is nobody got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.43,0:28:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are the losses?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.14,0:28:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The insurance will cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.10,0:28:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more worried about the damage to our image.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.02,0:28:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've asked the press to cooperate, and I'm sure they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.86,0:28:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who did it? And why our company?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.11,0:28:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may not be against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.28,0:28:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be someone who's mentally disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.08,0:28:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a man on the line, sir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.75,0:28:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He says he planted the bomb. - Have it put through.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.83,0:28:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put him through.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.63,0:28:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.80,0:28:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, we planted the bomb in your shopping centre.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.30,0:28:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We want $10 million.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.80,0:28:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pay up or your other properties will get bombed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.60,0:28:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.85,0:28:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.47,0:28:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a huge amount of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.64,0:28:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to call a board meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.48,0:28:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've got 24 hours. And don't coll the police.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.15,0:29:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What do we do, then? - Must be some kind of hoax.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.82,0:29:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.41,0:29:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.53,0:29:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We pay enough taxes. The police should do something for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.66,0:29:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Get me through to the chief. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.66,0:29:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raymond, you were extremely lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.00,0:29:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that no-one was hurt in the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.54,0:29:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.17,0:29:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Chu case... well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.34,0:29:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you. But it wasn't just me. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.51,0:29:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've proven yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.22,0:29:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should handle this case. Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.10,0:29:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sure. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.27,0:29:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very tough case.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.19,0:29:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they gave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.48,0:29:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in our department do you think can solve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.32,0:29:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.03,0:29:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.78,0:29:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.08,0:29:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we could bring back somebody who's on leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.46,0:29:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean somebody like Ka Kui?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.12,0:29:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has substantial experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.67,0:29:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.96,0:30:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's unorthodox, impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.21,0:30:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll only give us trouble. We have to bear the responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.51,0:30:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree he's a little bit rash, but underneath he's a good cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.51,0:30:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.68,0:30:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you think he's our man, you go and find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.77,0:30:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who's the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.20,0:30:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Over there. - Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.96,0:30:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fasten your seat belt, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.09,0:30:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot the sunscreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.76,0:30:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy it when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.64,0:30:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get your passport when you were younger?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.68,0:30:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out a call for Detective Chan Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.64,0:30:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.31,0:30:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your attention, please.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.69,0:31:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will Chan Ka Kui...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.40,0:31:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see. No, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.94,0:31:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's cute. - It's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.23,0:31:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Ka Kui please contact us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.19,0:31:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's you. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.24,0:31:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's up? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.91,0:31:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.37,0:31:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you Mr. Chan? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.87,0:31:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid there seems to be a problem with your passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.92,0:31:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.21,0:31:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just be a quick check.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.00,0:31:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.80,0:31:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.13,0:31:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.42,0:31:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.30,0:31:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.11,0:31:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.65,0:31:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.74,0:31:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? I have a plane waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.28,0:31:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.03,0:31:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the bombing case has become a blackmail case,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.99,0:31:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's a very tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.45,0:32:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-So? - This case is a real challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.50,0:32:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raymond was hoping...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.92,0:32:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping that you might cancel your holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.25,0:32:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I've already boarded the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.71,0:32:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I've quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.17,0:32:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.51,0:32:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been under a lot of pressure lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.85,0:32:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- But ducking out like this? - I'm not ducking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.35,0:32:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he's not ducking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.06,0:32:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raymond is a great admirer of your abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.52,0:32:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any abilities. I'm too impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.65,0:32:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impulsive? More like... a man of action!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.32,0:32:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could control my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.99,0:32:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A true man of action acts on instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.45,0:32:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the police force needs men with discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.79,0:32:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinctive men have to be unconventional,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.04,0:32:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even at the cost of discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.46,0:32:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you did everything by the book, no case would ever get solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.38,0:32:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Am I right? - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.34,0:32:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better get back on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.85,0:32:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.35,0:33:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.31,0:33:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much is the ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.65,0:33:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten million. That's all we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.32,0:33:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do we have any suspects? - Not a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.98,0:33:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think these people are insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.65,0:33:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking me? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.95,0:33:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you traced the dynamite?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.33,0:33:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why? - Yes, Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.79,0:33:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple. Dynamite is a controlled substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.17,0:33:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You either smuggle it in or you steal it from a local company.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.17,0:33:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. We hadn't thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.92,0:33:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must find their bomb factory before the company pays the ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.93,0:33:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that, we can foil their plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.47,0:33:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it you always solve problems so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.27,0:33:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're made for this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.52,0:33:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.36,0:33:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a plane to catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.36,0:33:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.61,0:33:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go there anytime. This case is once-in-a-lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.03,0:33:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go there next time. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.20,0:34:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better talk to May first.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.87,0:34:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.08,0:34:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry UP-
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.50,0:34:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Miss! - Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.00,0:34:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- My plane... - It just took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.84,0:34:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's taken off!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.43,0:34:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've missed your flight!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.18,0:34:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on them to stay on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.52,0:34:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have May's passport!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.52,0:34:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It sure isn't your lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.15,0:34:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.87,0:34:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Bill, we'd better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.66,0:34:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You all right? - I ate something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.00,0:34:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That way, sir. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.29,0:34:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. We're police officers. We're here to see Mr. Fung.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.38,0:34:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 30th floor. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.68,0:35:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bugging devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.22,0:35:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bug? Look out... Nixon lost his job because of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.64,0:35:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we want to solve the case, we have to know our targets well.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.48,0:35:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you. Put them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.32,0:35:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Wong, there are two police officers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.82,0:35:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where's the bathroom? - On your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.57,0:35:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.16,0:35:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-five, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.70,0:35:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-four, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.12,0:35:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.54,0:35:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Bill, I'm really worried about May.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.17,0:35:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call Jakarta Airport as soon as I get back to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.18,0:35:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.61,0:36:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be ashamed of yourself. Haven't you got any manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.12,0:36:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.09,0:36:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Chan to see Miss Wong.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.26,0:36:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Please wait. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.64,0:36:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ka Kui. - Uncle Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.52,0:36:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you were used to taking the blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.03,0:36:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.74,0:36:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.61,0:36:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Detective Chang. This is Detective Chan. {\i1}We...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.32,0:36:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Please come with me. - We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.37,0:36:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Mr. Fung is busy now, but he's signed the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.21,0:36:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.80,0:37:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Excuse me, where's the toilet? - Down the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.05,0:37:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.68,0:37:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.89,0:37:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Where's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.15,0:37:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a sudden urge.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.12,0:37:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.25,0:37:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That site is worth three billion. There would be a profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.58,0:37:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mr. Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.17,0:37:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Detective Chan is here. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.25,0:37:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.68,0:37:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're developing the new properties very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.44,0:38:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.53,0:38:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Directors, managers, and department heads, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.11,0:38:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've called this meeting to review the performance
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.12,0:38:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of our property portfolio over the last six months,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.62,0:38:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to set the sales target for the next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.25,0:38:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may all know that since the stock market collapse last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.63,0:38:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Hang Seng Index has risen 66%.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.63,0:38:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you the performance of the major blue chip shares.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.28,0:38:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, given the performance of the bank and property sectors,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.66,0:39:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the outlook of the stock market for the next six months remains uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.33,0:39:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In situations like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.38,0:39:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,small investors are likely to put their money in property.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.77,0:39:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we have to accelerate the pace of our new housing developments.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.53,0:39:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.54,0:39:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone asks the chairman for this, it's $500 to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.13,0:39:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.59,0:39:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.38,0:39:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What happened? - It's a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.72,0:39:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you plant the bugs? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.18,0:39:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And the desk? - All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.18,0:39:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Was it easy? - He wasn't against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.35,0:40:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What did they say? - Something about houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.52,0:40:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.56,0:40:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where are you going? - I'll take the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.72,0:40:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.60,0:40:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, you're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.56,0:40:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.93,0:40:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.44,0:40:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.61,0:40:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... you didn't want me to come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.77,0:40:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left me there and took my passport!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.44,0:40:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I got there, I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.24,0:40:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I was sent back here, they detained me for ten hours in a cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.29,0:41:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I keep my voice down?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.70,0:41:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you take your dog for a walk, do you not take him home afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.34,0:41:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm even worse than a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.00,0:41:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, they're watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.67,0:41:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.47,0:41:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.97,0:41:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to tell me in front of everyone what you think I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.43,0:41:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you take me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.02,0:41:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.94,0:41:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.69,0:41:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.36,0:41:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, why do you treat me this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.86,0:41:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You treat strangers better than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.45,0:41:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.08,0:41:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's over between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.72,0:41:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chan Ka Kui, I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.81,0:42:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Bill, did you make that call?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.43,0:42:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to go to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.35,0:42:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've ruined my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.62,0:42:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.70,0:42:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away or I'll run you over.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.20,0:42:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Go away! - Don't be childish!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.92,0:42:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't grab my bag! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.21,0:42:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even touch me. Go away. Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.96,0:42:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.63,0:42:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.72,0:42:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've nothing else to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.05,0:42:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.14,0:42:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.02,0:42:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me. Don't touch my motorbike.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.81,0:42:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep away. I don't want you anywhere near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.73,0:42:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let me explain. - Keep away.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.90,0:42:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.32,0:43:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep away from me. I never want to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.62,0:43:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.96,0:43:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, get back to work. I want to see Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.46,0:43:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, the boss wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.14,0:43:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.93,0:43:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.94,0:43:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to call May to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.90,0:43:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.48,0:43:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't explain anything to women! This is my way to handle 'em...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.36,0:43:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if a man's not at home, it's obvious he's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.36,0:43:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I have to go to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.99,0:43:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pay any attention to his chauvinism. Go and get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.27,0:44:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.32,0:44:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than wasting my time here. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.03,0:44:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I walk you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.41,0:44:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.16,0:44:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.04,0:44:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.83,0:44:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me, it's me you want. Don't be foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.34,0:44:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're in this together. - Don't try anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.96,0:44:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.26,0:44:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really had you going! I got the both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.23,0:44:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.41,0:45:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.42,0:45:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.34,0:45:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I thought it was just a simple game, I wouldn't call my men to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.93,0:45:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.26,0:45:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My boss asked me to teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.39,0:45:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting paid to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.64,0:45:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't need to dirty my hands. My men can take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.77,0:45:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.07,0:45:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give you a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.23,0:45:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you apologise to Mr. Ko now, we won't break both of your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.61,0:45:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just break one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.20,0:45:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the bullshit. Go on, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.62,0:45:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill a cop? I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.75,0:45:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My boss wants to teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.50,0:45:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ripping a few limbs off should do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.42,0:46:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.39,0:46:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.56,0:46:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is. Beat him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.21,0:47:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, finish him off. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.69,0:48:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move over. Let me drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.54,0:48:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn you into mashed banana.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.64,0:49:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't my fault! I was paid to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.29,0:49:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep away or I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.92,0:49:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.00,0:49:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'll shoot. - Shoot here!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.46,0:49:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.64,0:49:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not. It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.31,0:49:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I'll kick your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.94,0:49:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.53,0:49:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.78,0:49:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.82,0:50:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.33,0:50:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.12,0:50:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you chase him? That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.25,0:50:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to make things up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.54,0:50:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it had been acid in that pistol and not ink...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.17,0:50:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be scarred for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.22,0:50:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they wanted to distract you and then kidnap me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.18,0:50:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.18,0:50:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, I want my boyfriend to be gentle, not a savage.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.07,0:50:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.12,0:50:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.87,0:50:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Police Detective in Park Rumpus." Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.63,0:50:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.38,0:50:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check out the surveillance team.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.43,0:51:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ACTIVE-DUTY POLICEMAN INVOLVED IN 10-MAN PARK BRAWL
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.44,0:51:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me. Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.86,0:51:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Chu wants revenge, but don't take the law into your own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.82,0:51:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.61,0:51:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.58,0:51:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.99,0:51:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can cope with it. I just want them to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.83,0:51:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. But keep your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.87,0:51:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we've got a surveillance team.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.88,0:51:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're very good. Go and talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.64,0:51:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he give you an earful? Did he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.56,0:51:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.85,0:51:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just wants to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.23,0:51:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can somebody show off if they don't have an audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.79,0:52:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.33,0:52:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.79,0:52:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Detective Chan Ka Kui. Detective Ng, Detective Mui.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.59,0:52:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.71,0:52:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys introduce yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.38,0:52:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Special Tactical Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.01,0:52:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.35,0:52:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have great expertise in tracking targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.18,0:52:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? Will this be useful for the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.27,0:52:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we don't even know who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.81,0:52:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.23,0:52:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow anyone suspicious, and then you'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.90,0:52:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.94,0:52:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can find the their hiding place for making bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.28,0:52:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could follow them during the transaction, then arrest them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.45,0:52:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That simple? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.49,0:52:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. That's why I always have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.04,0:52:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope you have a smooth collaboration.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.54,0:52:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Ng, could I have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.13,0:52:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be room for you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.67,0:52:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.75,0:52:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.80,0:53:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Detective Chan. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.55,0:53:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.89,0:53:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.32,0:53:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.86,0:53:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fung said his shares would go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.45,0:53:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's hardly relevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.57,0:53:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his girlfriend is a supermodel!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.83,0:53:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.37,0:53:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it. You go and call May.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.67,0:53:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.13,0:53:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui! Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.43,0:53:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your conditions have been presented to the board,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.60,0:53:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they have agreed to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.93,0:53:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No shit. Do you have the money?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.06,0:53:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have it all. $10 million is a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.11,0:53:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trace it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.57,0:54:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Tai Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.70,0:54:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.84,0:54:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on Ting Kok Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.43,0:54:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HQ, calling all foot patrols. Are there any units on Ting Kok Road, over?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.27,0:54:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is PC 12674 on Ting Kok Road, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.94,0:54:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PC 12674,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.11,0:54:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,check anybody leaving a phone box in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.32,0:54:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you stalling for time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.82,0:54:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we didn't call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.12,0:54:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now we want 20 million.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.83,0:54:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty million! Such a huge sum.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.42,0:55:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Find it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.25,0:55:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.30,0:55:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is PC 12674.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.60,0:55:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anything?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.64,0:55:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've got a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.39,0:55:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. He's very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.18,0:55:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He could be armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.14,0:55:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep everything low key.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.11,0:55:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. You're supposed to use the pedestrian crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.99,0:55:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Move along. - Give me a chance, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.79,0:55:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see your ID card?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.68,0:55:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calling HQ...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.35,0:55:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}PC 12674, do you copy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.53,0:56:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An officer needs assistance on Ting Kok Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.87,0:56:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, he isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.87,0:56:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.87,0:56:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way things go. It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.71,0:56:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been in uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.21,0:56:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.01,0:56:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're excused.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.34,0:56:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I get in trouble for losing my gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.51,0:56:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about promotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.76,0:56:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.01,0:56:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you learn from the experience, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.39,0:56:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It happens to every cop. - It won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.56,0:56:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'd recognise him?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.19,0:56:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.32,0:56:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.90,0:56:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could do with someone like you on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.86,0:56:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.24,0:56:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Can you file this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.74,0:56:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}Hello. - It's Joker.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.62,0:57:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Go ahead. {\i1}- News.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.12,0:57:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What news?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.20,0:57:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A guy called Crazy Fai sells dynamite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.25,0:57:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nine o'clock, Hoi Wong Bar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.18,0:57:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you know what we'll do next? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.77,0:57:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.61,0:57:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What do you want? - Are you Fai? I want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.28,0:57:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.24,0:57:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.78,0:57:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.54,0:57:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.13,0:57:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's your name? - Lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.13,0:57:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.42,0:57:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.38,0:57:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explosives?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.47,0:57:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.05,0:57:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What are they for? - Fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.76,0:58:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look like a fisherman.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.68,0:58:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I told you it was for business?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.68,0:58:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a good price. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.56,0:58:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right... but I need to speak to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.23,0:58:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my stuff. Don't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.24,0:58:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.17,0:58:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, he's out of stock, but he'll call me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.76,0:58:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here, I'll be back when I've finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.93,0:58:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.77,0:59:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you. Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.23,0:59:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.36,0:59:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CID. On your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.08,0:59:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.04,0:59:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I only came here for a drink. - A drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.29,0:59:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard you were dealing contraband.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.42,0:59:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eyes front.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.81,1:00:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.64,1:00:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw me your gun. Quick!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.85,1:00:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.65,1:00:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy. Don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.62,1:00:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.16,1:00:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.44,1:01:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.61,1:01:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You screwed me over, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.15,1:01:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you call the cops?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.36,1:01:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.91,1:01:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.75,1:01:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.29,1:01:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you double-cross me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.58,1:01:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make sure you weren't a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.67,1:02:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I called the cops, to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.84,1:02:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get what you need.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.13,1:02:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.30,1:02:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you got the money?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.97,1:02:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cash on delivery.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.48,1:02:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep a lookout.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.04,1:02:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good stuff?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.29,1:02:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the quarries.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.16,1:02:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got any more?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.29,1:02:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, plenty.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.92,1:02:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's enough to blow up the Empire State Building.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.89,1:02:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just met him! I've never seen him before!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.93,1:02:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can get away?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.60,1:03:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.15,1:03:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.99,1:03:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two spoons of sugar?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.57,1:03:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.91,1:03:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The temperature okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.33,1:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.92,1:03:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is stretching the law. If I were him, I'd clam up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.00,1:03:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem comfortable. Will you cooperate with us now?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.76,1:03:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooperate?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.22,1:03:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to die?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.34,1:03:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cooperate, you can walk out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.64,1:03:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep everything secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.14,1:03:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If need be, we'll keep you under protection.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.93,1:03:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you three could protect me the rest of my life,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.85,1:03:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I would consider it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.40,1:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.98,1:03:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we were to release you now,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.86,1:03:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we might, say, "find" drugs on you after you were gone,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.62,1:03:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or maybe "discover" you've been molesting young girls.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.12,1:03:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this get you good results?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.66,1:04:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. It never fails.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.05,1:04:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the charge?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.51,1:04:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen a lot worse than this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.97,1:04:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play along before I'll go to jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.78,1:04:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all seem like nice young ladies!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.91,1:04:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you not seen anything like this before?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.16,1:04:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop! I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.54,1:04:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.34,1:04:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice young ladies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.51,1:04:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to play along?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.06,1:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sue you!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.97,1:05:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.64,1:05:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guns have a way of going off when you least expect it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.65,1:05:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just say it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.65,1:05:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Escaped prisoner!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.86,1:05:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escaped prisoner!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.98,1:05:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.36,1:05:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why didn't you say so? Come on, sit down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.57,1:05:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- Cigarette? - No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.37,1:05:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are men in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.67,1:05:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shaw's over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.34,1:05:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have sold three explosives lately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.17,1:05:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One buyer named Xing, he was u fisherman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.68,1:05:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've known him a long time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.14,1:05:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He bought it to blast reef fish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.10,1:05:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other guy buys my stuff to refill empty bullet shell cases{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.72,1:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so he can sell them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.56,1:05:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he's only bought a few.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.19,1:05:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The third guy's name was Polar Bear. He's a big-time dealer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.52,1:05:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He usually hangs out at the Yaumatei Pool Hull.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.43,1:06:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.97,1:06:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target's in a taxi. It's DP5608.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.89,1:06:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Big Mouth?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.48,1:06:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi number DP5608, heading north to Kok Road.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.11,1:06:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Copy, Big Mouth. I see target DP5608.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.20,1:06:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's headed to TST Metro Station.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.91,1:06:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All copy. All copy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.37,1:06:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Renew info. Get to TST Metro Station.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.04,1:08:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Target on metro heading to Kung Tong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.75,1:08:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.46,1:08:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stay there. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.12,1:08:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target off metro.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.46,1:09:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Target in taxi CW721, heading to industrial area.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.47,1:09:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target out of the car, heading to Yat Sing Street.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.26,1:09:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Copy. Over. Sun, your team leaves first.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.31,1:09:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Car to Yat Sing Street.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.10,1:09:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start supervision. Wait for orders.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.02,1:09:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.66,1:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.21,1:10:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, buddy, where is Pak Lok Street?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.17,1:10:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No idea. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.59,1:10:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone carrying two bags heading your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.44,1:10:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Polar Bear.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.35,1:10:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went shopping?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.02,1:10:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you followed?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.07,1:10:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.86,1:10:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Open up.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.11,1:10:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.38,1:11:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Chan, it's him. These must be the guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.34,1:11:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three voices.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.69,1:11:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louder, let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.48,1:11:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother, stop waiting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.40,1:11:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything ready?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.11,1:11:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.62,1:11:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I have to make a call.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.13,1:11:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not here. Make sure we're not being bugged.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.51,1:11:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Find a place at the TST. Make sure everything is fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.84,1:11:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't waste time. Get going.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.90,1:12:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three people.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.40,1:12:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- They're coming out. - Roger.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.99,1:12:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You don't deserve this. - You don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.26,1:12:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check the plates and follow the van.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.68,1:12:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here. I'll go and take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.73,1:12:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.70,1:12:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.03,1:13:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.66,1:13:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where are you going? - To take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.70,1:13:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Be careful. - I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.83,1:13:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.54,1:13:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Chan, they've shaken off our unit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.58,1:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, they'll come back. Call them off.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.42,1:13:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.19,1:15:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.82,1:15:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.87,1:15:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.95,1:15:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I fell over. - Someone's up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.51,1:16:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.77,1:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.61,1:16:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.36,1:16:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy must be deaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.82,1:16:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see three men come through here a few hours ago?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.75,1:16:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ask him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.17,1:16:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you work here?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.01,1:16:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you sleep here?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.90,1:16:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I can't communicate with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.03,1:17:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got an answer, but I have no idea what it means.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.40,1:17:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ask him.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.74,1:17:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him down to the station.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.37,1:17:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. You're coming with me for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.29,1:17:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come along. It won't cost anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.70,1:17:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need for cuffs.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.29,1:17:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you collect such things?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.92,1:17:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's deaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.01,1:17:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all these toys in here yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.59,1:18:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Freeze! - He can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.47,1:18:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.03,1:18:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.45,1:18:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a deaf-mute running around. Find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.92,1:18:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.79,1:18:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know he could fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.59,1:18:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither did I. Go and find my gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.84,1:18:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.51,1:18:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can manage to finance the buyout of Indian Ocean Bank,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.84,1:18:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be a welcome addition to our portfolio.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.43,1:18:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fung, telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.43,1:18:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no calls.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.35,1:18:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but it's that man again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.19,1:19:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.44,1:19:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.71,1:19:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You called the cops.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.17,1:19:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you must be mistaken. We haven't!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.34,1:19:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You needn't try and deceive us. We knew you'd go to the cops.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.71,1:19:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To make you abandon that idea,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.34,1:19:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we will demonstrate our power to you tomorrow at 12:00.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.18,1:19:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't waste time bargaining with you ever again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.14,1:19:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After 12:00 tomorrow, if you decide it's prudent to pay the $20 million,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.14,1:19:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}place an ad in the name of your Zhiye Group{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.15,1:19:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in one of the major newspapers the day after tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.28,1:19:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Mr. Lam!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.74,1:19:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After 12:00 tomorrow, if you decide it's prudent to pay the $20 million,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.78,1:19:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}place an ad in the name of your Zhiye Group{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.29,1:19:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in one of the major newspapers the day after tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.87,1:19:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.04,1:19:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was the call from?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.54,1:20:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a modified mobile phone, so we couldn't trace it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.38,1:20:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We knew you'd go to the cops.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.55,1:20:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To make you abandon that idea,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.63,1:20:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we will demonstrate our power to you tomorrow at 12:00.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.88,1:20:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't waste time bargaining with you ever again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.93,1:20:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, they're bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.72,1:20:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've sent extra officers to protect your buildings.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.56,1:20:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.56,1:20:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.65,1:20:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will never tolerate such an outrage! It's time to act!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.48,1:20:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.99,1:20:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fay!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.87,1:20:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.33,1:20:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Polar Bear.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.04,1:20:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ken. He'd like a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.33,1:20:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't snitch on you!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.96,1:20:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then why did they turn up after you got caught?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.09,1:20:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why did they let you go so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.21,1:20:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lack of evidence. They granted me bail.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.72,1:20:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't snitch, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.93,1:20:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all the same to us. We don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.43,1:21:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where are we going? - Make any difference?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.35,1:21:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Miss Wong. - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.69,1:21:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- We've checked the mail. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.52,1:21:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And these are for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.52,1:21:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who on earth sent those?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.86,1:21:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know. Someone special, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.69,1:21:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't know, who would?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.36,1:21:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.99,1:21:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plant this bomb and we're even.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.87,1:21:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do the job or you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.21,1:21:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where shall I put it? - I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.71,1:21:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.97,1:21:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. Thanks a lot. Keep an eye out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.39,1:21:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.61,1:21:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cop. What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.40,1:21:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.67,1:22:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ID card.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.71,1:22:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.21,1:22:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.89,1:22:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CID. Your case.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.35,1:22:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.03,1:22:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.24,1:22:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.82,1:22:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.41,1:22:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. CID. May I see your bag?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.30,1:22:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The red bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.63,1:22:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. CID.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.69,1:23:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.86,1:23:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It should be fine. - Here's the mail, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.87,1:23:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.78,1:23:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it's a bluff?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.24,1:23:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so, but we can't be sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.62,1:23:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Keep in touch.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.38,1:23:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.09,1:23:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask her to wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.72,1:23:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.14,1:23:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, May's downstairs. She wants to talk to you urgently.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.47,1:23:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.02,1:23:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.07,1:23:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've written a letter for you. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.61,1:24:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May. You came all this way to give me this?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.62,1:24:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's important, so keep it safe. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.62,1:24:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, where's the scooter?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.66,1:24:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't get along, so I sold it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.67,1:24:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow her.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.56,1:24:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my backup units in position.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.86,1:24:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I think they're bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.53,1:24:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should depend on the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.86,1:24:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.65,1:24:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.49,1:24:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.54,1:24:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the fire extinguisher.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.83,1:24:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Mr. Lam.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.22,1:25:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.06,1:25:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Go and investigate. - Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.19,1:25:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic. Ka Kui, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.19,1:25:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the fire department. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.61,1:25:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring a fire extinguisher.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.37,1:25:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Put the fire out first.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.50,1:25:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, get moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.79,1:25:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is the ambulance here? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.25,1:25:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go call them!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.42,1:25:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need more help.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.01,1:25:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Phone, sir. - Bill, you take the phone call.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.51,1:25:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, meet me upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.52,1:25:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought you were supposed to protect me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.61,1:26:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.69,1:26:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Package bomb. Miss Wong lost an arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.70,1:26:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ZHIYE GROUP, TOGETHER WITH EVERY HONG KONG CITIZEN,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.12,1:26:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,STRIVES TO PRESERVE THE BEAUTY OF HONG KONG
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.05,1:26:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How's Miss Wong? - She's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.42,1:26:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor said her arm would recover.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.47,1:26:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll do a skin graft on her face later.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.10,1:26:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.68,1:26:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wong's decided to pay up.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.02,1:26:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to tell Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.86,1:26:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Bill, that's the way it goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.03,1:26:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always said it was going to be a tough case.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.86,1:26:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with well-organised criminals here.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.24,1:26:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they'd blown me up instead. I don't like putting lives at risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.54,1:26:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.29,1:26:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they come to collect the money, I'm sure we'll get them.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.62,1:26:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I pass on what you said to Raymond, he won't be happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.75,1:27:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we need is real action.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.38,1:27:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.59,1:27:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you've seen the papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.22,1:27:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what do I tell the Chief?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.64,1:27:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way it goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.65,1:27:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always said it'd be a tough case.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.73,1:27:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with well-organised criminals here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.28,1:27:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they'd blown me up instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.91,1:27:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like putting lives at risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.41,1:27:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.87,1:27:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they come to collect the money, I'm sure we'll get them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.41,1:27:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this is talk. What we need is some real action.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.89,1:27:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somethings up. Raymond's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.02,1:27:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way it goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.69,1:28:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always said it'd be a tough case.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.11,1:28:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with well-organised criminals here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.36,1:28:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they'd blown me up instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.99,1:28:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like putting lives at risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.78,1:28:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.08,1:28:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they come to collect, I'm sure we'll get them.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.54,1:28:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your situation, and I'll note it in the report.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.33,1:28:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with the case.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.18,1:28:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You come, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.81,1:28:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.43,1:28:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you two have a fight?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.44,1:28:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. But this is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.16,1:28:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.74,1:28:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get him!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.99,1:28:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.62,1:29:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.37,1:29:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it through.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.21,1:29:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Put it through.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.00,1:29:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}Hello? - Ka Kui.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.46,1:29:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May's been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.05,1:29:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.13,1:29:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd just left the shop when someone dragged her into a van.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.55,1:29:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.14,1:29:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But it must have something to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.56,1:29:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be those thugs again?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.52,1:29:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chu Tu.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.40,1:29:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ka Kui! Hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.07,1:29:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ka Kui! What's up? - An old score. May's been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.20,1:29:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.70,1:29:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What happened? - May's been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.33,1:29:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Sign this cheque before you're dead. Our brothers...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.87,1:29:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Please stop. He's a patient. - Let me finish.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.96,1:29:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did what you asked. That's why we deserve something.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.54,1:29:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't need any money when you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.89,1:30:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chu Tu!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.94,1:30:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Chu Tu! - Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.10,1:30:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chu Tu!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.61,1:30:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring May back!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.94,1:30:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know nothing! I did nothing! It's him! Him!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.99,1:30:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring May back!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.37,1:31:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, you can't do that to a patient! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.33,1:31:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put him down!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.87,1:31:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak up! What have you done with May?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.50,1:31:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I didn't take her. - Who did, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.08,1:31:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very nasty to you before... but now I'm sick and penniless.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.54,1:31:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What reason would I have for taking her?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.96,1:31:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he did have any money, he'd be pouring it into treatment.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.30,1:31:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is none of our doing. Hassling you was business, not personal.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.18,1:31:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only did it on account of the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.72,1:31:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.02,1:31:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a phone over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.06,1:31:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die before you sign this!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.90,1:31:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! I've had about enough of you!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.15,1:31:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got one foot in the grave, so what do I care?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.87,1:31:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello, this is 1378. - Ka {\i1}Kui!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.08,1:31:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.75,1:31:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You recognise her voice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.34,1:31:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're at the Hung Fung Industrial Building.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.59,1:31:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.68,1:32:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come alone or she's dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.59,1:32:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.64,1:32:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.02,1:32:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know where that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.22,1:32:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.89,1:32:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.39,1:32:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.69,1:32:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.94,1:32:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay. Why have you kidnapped her?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.15,1:32:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ka Kui, by the time you read this letter..."
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.23,1:32:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.32,1:33:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...I've decided we should be apart."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.49,1:33:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.78,1:33:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't think I'll see you again."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.58,1:33:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a love letter!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.95,1:33:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like they say... unlucky in love, lucky in money.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.87,1:33:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.88,1:33:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.21,1:33:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"When we first met, I thought you liked your job very much,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.42,1:33:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"and you'd be my Mr. Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.34,1:33:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Now I realise the only thing that matters in your life is your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.56,1:33:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I tell myself what made me fall in love with you
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.10,1:33:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"is also what makes me want to leave you."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.56,1:33:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, why? Why did you break up?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.24,1:33:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You told me you didn't want me involved with your work,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.57,1:33:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"but I didn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.08,1:33:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What I did mind, though, is that you never spent enough time with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.91,1:33:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Being with you was the happiest time of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.66,1:33:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But when you weren't there, it was the worst time of my life."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.25,1:33:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.63,1:34:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If I didn't leave you,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.96,1:34:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'd spend my life waiting for you to come home!"
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.55,1:34:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you stop it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.89,1:34:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's crying!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.43,1:34:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is he.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.35,1:34:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep reading, go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.11,1:34:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...because you can never stop being a policeman."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.32,1:34:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A policeman who never stops.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.70,1:34:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.07,1:34:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I think it's the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.74,1:34:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please forgive me for making such a selfish choice. May."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.88,1:34:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.96,1:34:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want you to help us get rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.84,1:34:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have heard the Zhiye Group was blackmailed.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.76,1:34:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hardest part of the job is the pick-up.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.39,1:34:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll collect the ransom for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.10,1:34:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.40,1:34:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.98,1:35:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said no.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.87,1:35:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'll enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.04,1:35:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.21,1:35:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.17,1:35:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.79,1:35:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.26,1:35:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.80,1:35:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.89,1:35:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.73,1:35:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to play the hero?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.58,1:35:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.47,1:36:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.90,1:36:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rotten swine!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.65,1:36:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.03,1:36:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me if you've got the guts.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.15,1:36:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tough!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.03,1:36:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Let's see if his girl is tough, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.37,1:36:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.67,1:36:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that? How's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.26,1:36:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! You've made your point.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.09,1:36:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you'll do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.01,1:36:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let her go. I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.77,1:37:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let her go unless you help us.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.23,1:37:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.77,1:37:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Collect the money for us. Then I'll let you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.44,1:37:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.24,1:37:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.41,1:37:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.69,1:37:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't advise you to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.65,1:37:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break one wire and the whole thing blows.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.19,1:37:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing happens if I press this button.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.16,1:38:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.51,1:38:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.73,1:38:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.23,1:38:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.79,1:38:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.16,1:38:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's on the line. - Trace the call!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.04,1:38:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get Uncle Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.38,1:38:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the money ready? We'll collect it in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.76,1:38:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.97,1:38:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you call the cops? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.02,1:39:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ka Kui?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.06,1:39:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.77,1:39:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he be so irresponsible?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.86,1:39:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait. Don't take any risks.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.16,1:39:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.25,1:39:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have ten minutes to get back here again.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.71,1:39:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No tricks.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.17,1:39:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't get our money, your vest will go bang!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.51,1:39:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.22,1:39:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.39,1:39:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.40,1:39:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.44,1:39:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.66,1:40:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Fung. - Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.07,1:40:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.58,1:40:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.71,1:40:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised to let us bug the phones.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.08,1:40:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could trace the calls.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.17,1:40:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad you can't handle the bomb case so effectively.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.09,1:40:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have everything ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.55,1:40:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they pay the money, we move into action.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.13,1:40:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you won't do anything to make matters worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.47,1:40:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this will encourage the bombers.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.47,1:40:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the police couldn't help. We could only depend on ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.48,1:40:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, the boss was looking...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.11,1:40:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.69,1:40:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.82,1:40:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ka Kui! - Out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.11,1:40:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.37,1:40:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.99,1:40:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.79,1:40:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.25,1:40:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.67,1:40:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.51,1:41:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. I'm here to collect the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.13,1:41:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.64,1:41:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is he your man? - Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.06,1:41:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.27,1:41:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time. The money!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.36,1:41:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What are you doing? - Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.11,1:41:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move and I'll shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.66,1:41:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.07,1:41:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.49,1:41:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.62,1:41:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you shoot me, everybody here...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.67,1:41:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be blown sky high.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.88,1:41:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one wire breaks, the whole thing will explode!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.13,1:41:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.38,1:41:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we work this out?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.22,1:41:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't leave here in ten minutes, it will go off.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.93,1:41:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.28,1:42:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.12,1:42:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention all units! Do not stop Ka Kui.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.84,1:42:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui! Ka Kui!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.63,1:42:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.18,1:42:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.11,1:42:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I think he did it. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.57,1:42:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Looks like he was followed. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.52,1:43:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him to move up.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.32,1:43:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.40,1:43:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being followed. Let me shake them off first.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.24,1:43:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.83,1:43:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the cops behind us?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.64,1:43:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back! Don't come near!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.11,1:44:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you stop here?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.74,1:44:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What are you doing? - What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.78,1:44:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb's about to blow. Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.12,1:44:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb! Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.39,1:44:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no cops!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.72,1:44:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow him to bits.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.52,1:44:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What about the money?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.02,1:44:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can't get a radio signal in the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.81,1:44:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.86,1:44:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- We've got the girl. Don't worry. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.67,1:46:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything goes wrong, kill her.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.98,1:47:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is May?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.53,1:47:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.01,1:47:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, he's back.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.39,1:48:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you he wouldn't play tricks.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.79,1:48:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.80,1:48:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.68,1:48:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze! You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.23,1:48:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.98,1:48:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on then, arrest us.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.36,1:48:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.32,1:48:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move and I'll shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.36,1:49:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? You'd have to shoot fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.45,1:49:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.16,1:49:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.49,1:49:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't shoot you, you'll only spend a few years in jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.20,1:49:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you'll be a reformed person. That's better than dying in this condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.91,1:49:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better to die than to live as a pauper. We are ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.63,1:49:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.84,1:49:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no shame in wanting wealth. But your way is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.72,1:49:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what is right and what is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.01,1:49:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can get everything you want in life
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.64,1:49:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by helping other people get what they want in life.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.02,1:49:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd have a whole new outlook. That's what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.19,1:49:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you have done now has hurt society.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.27,1:49:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This benefits no-one. - What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.82,1:49:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than you guys, who thinks you're doing the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.65,1:49:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would think highly of your purpose?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.33,1:49:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.66,1:49:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.50,1:49:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound too bad... but there's still one question.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.16,1:49:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might take your advice if we had certain opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.67,1:49:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, we don't want to go to jail.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.34,1:50:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to be punished.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.01,1:50:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push me!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.76,1:50:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! This is a fireworks factory.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.53,1:52:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- May! - I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.82,1:52:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.08,1:52:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.69,1:53:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.41,1:53:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui! Come here! There's the rubbish chute.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.17,1:53:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an exit.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.14,1:53:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, you go first.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.18,1:53:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks too high.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.02,1:53:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just jump!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.04,1:54:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka Kui, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.96,1:54:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. Get out of here, May. Go as far as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.67,1:54:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.15,1:56:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like it? Want some more? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.32,1:56:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about some more, you little bastard?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.11,1:56:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some more?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.32,1:56:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some more? Here!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.66,1:56:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some more?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.17,1:56:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.83,1:57:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.06,1:58:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.48,1:58:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. The fireworks are beautiful.

